# Trivy ignore list for catalog image scans.
#
# Each entry is a CVE id on its own line. Add a comment line above
# explaining why the finding is acceptable and a revisit date. Drop
# the entry once the upstream image ships a fix tag and the catalog
# bump lands.
#
# Format example:
#   # CVE-2099-12345 -- glibc in nextcloud base; upstream pending fix.
#   # Revisit: 2026-06-15. Mitigated by no public network exposure.
#   CVE-2099-12345
